<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200914/859578ba9aa442cea4b7c6237dabf80c.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">张永敬《兰亭思》</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200914/ee65610fe3524e69abc95ea1d1e8336f.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">张永敬《乾坤初探》</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200914/063201c8638148a783afff4a38477d75.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">张永敬《荣华千秋》</span></img></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200914/58597bc9ec564d4b9d2c41968b19a2d9.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">张永敬《润物无声》</span></img></p>
